      "description": "The Innovator Index Autocallable Income Strategy ETF (ACII) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in income alternatives. The fund is actively managed. The fund employs a combination of OTC autocallable swap agreements on three major US equity ETFs, laddered over different dates in attempt to generate income and provide a small cushion on the downside risks. ACII was launched on Sep 25, 2025 and is issued by Innovator.",
